Provide Personalized Experiences With Einstein Personalization

Use Einstein Personalization to deliver timely, relevant, personalized experiences. As a new Customer 360 application built on Data Cloud, Einstein Personalization provides AI-based recommendations and personalized content to customers or site visitors in real time.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, Performance, and Developer editions.

When: This feature is available on a restricted basis in Summer â€™24. Contact your Account Executive for more information.

How: Einstein Personalization requires the installation and configuration of Data Cloud. Using foundational Data Cloud elements, like real-time data ingestion, identity resolution, calculated insights, and data graphs, Einstein Personalization can deliver relevant, targeted, individualized content to customers at the right time. Einstein Personalization also gathers and displays metrics to provide insights into the usage and effectiveness of personalized decisions.
